      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car is an absolute gem\u2014truly in showroom condition. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only taking it out on those perfect, sunny Sunday afternoons. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, crisp feel inside. It\u2019s easily the cleanest example you\u2019ll find out there. I\u2019m looking for a good home for it, so come on by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
